    "description": "The playbook recommends documented individual routes; it is not an enforcement allowlist. User-directed scripts, plugins, and host capabilities stay outside plugin scope. Provider entries never classify or veto host browser/computer use.",
    "catalogRole": "advisory. This catalog records routes documented as permitted by each provider for individuals. It is never an allowlist or refusal basis. Attended browser/computer use in the athlete's own visible authenticated session is always a valid athlete-selected route for any provider with a web app, for reads and for approval-gated writes, whenever the host exposes that capability."
  },
